# {{projectName}}

NestJS modular backend generated with [@nakedev/nest-scaffold](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@nakedev/nest-scaffold).

## Setup

```bash
pnpm install
cp .env.example .env
{{#if docker}}docker compose up -d{{/if}}
pnpm run start:dev
```

{{#if swagger}}Swagger: http://localhost:3000/api{{/if}}

## Scripts

- `pnpm run start:dev` — development with watch
- `pnpm run build` — compile
- `pnpm run test` — unit tests
{{#if e2e}}- `pnpm run test:e2e` — e2e tests{{/if}}
{{#if seeds}}- `pnpm run seed` — seed database{{/if}}

## Generate modules

```bash
nest-scaffold generate module orders
```
